So yeah, I'm back from the dead and I'm gonna try to take a new step again. Thank y'all to those people who reached out and thank you as well to those who disappointed me. May God bless y'all.

sorry for the long thread :3

I'm a little bit disappointed tho. It took me some time to process things but I really am disappointed to some people. Those people that I put my faith it that they'll have my back when I'm at my lowest are those same people who left me in air. Surprisingly haha
Up to this day, I still don't know how that knife didn't work. I was sure that I put force in cutting my wrist tho. Maybe it's a miracle or a work of some deities, idk.
I even have a hard time chatting to someone privately now. It's just recently that I started chatting in our school gc again.

Some of the messages are from those people that I wasn't even expecting to care about me. There's even this one message from someone saying how my story before inspired her.

So yeah, after that I've been lowkey to all my accounts. I didn't have the courage to be public again

I can't really remember what happened next after that. All I remember is waking up feeling nothing. Checked my phone, opened my messenger and saw a lot of messages that until today, I haven't replied yet.
I chatted my bffs saying I'm okay and told them what my fam said to me.

Or should've just continued to take my own life. I was devastated.

After hearing those words from them, my tears dried up. Went upstairs and return to my room feeling empty. I don't have the desire to kill myself nor to continue to live. Just emptiness

and ran downstairs. Obviously my family saw me. They asked me what happened and there I told them everything and what I just did. I was expecting them to comfort me but what I got in return was the opposite. They told me that I shouldn't have been born

9:48 pm is when I decided to finally do it. Slashed my wrist with the knife but some unexpected thing happened. Idk why but I wasn't hurt by the knife. No wound, no blood. And after that, all these emotions rushed through my veins that I immediately threw the knife
I can feel my phone blowing up that time with messages, calls from everyone but I didn't even bother checking. I sat down there for hours still holding the knife and ready to take my own life

Idk what went on my mind but I started messaging those who are dear to me ( at least I consider them dear idk if they feel the same). After messaging I put down my phone and stared at my ceiling and started to cry.

I didn't care. Nothing is entering my brain. No sadness, no hesitation etc. The single thing on my mind that time was I'm going to kill myself.
went to my bedroom, locked the door, grabbed my pocket knife and sat down on the floor.

And immediately, I decided to kill myself. I chatted my bffs that I'm tired and I'm 100% ready to take my own life. Obviously they asked and told me what happened but I didn't say. They told me not to do it, as expected but my mind was blank at that time.

July 15, 2021 at exactly 6:24 PM is when I 100% decided to kill myself. I just got home from going out with my bestfriends and I wasn't expecting my day to turn upside down when I got home. Some personal thing happened at home to the point where I got really fed up

So fast forward sa ending. I'm still suicidal at that point pero may sinabi sya na sakin na nagdalawang isip ako. Not gonna say it but yun nalang ang pinanghahawakan ko ngayon.
I literally cried for 2 hrs straight to the point na wala nang lumalabas na luha.
Nilabas ko lahat ng mga hinanakit ko sa buhay. Kung ano yung tingin ko sa sarili ko, kung gano ko dina down yung sarili ko at kung gano ako ka trash para sa sarili ko.

So fast forward. We went sa kitchen to have a 1 on 1 talk. Di ko alam pano magsimula at di ko alam ano sasabihin but ewan nailabas ko lahat. I apologized for what happened between us 5 years ago. She cried, I cried and she accepted my apology

"Ma I'm tired. I want to die right now" that exact line lang yung nasabi ko that moment and napaiyak si mama. She hugged me so tight. I never got hugged by my mom that hard before. Feel na feel ko na natatakot syang mawala ako. Na fefeel ko na importante ako

Pagdating ko sa bahay eh si mama nag open ng door. Wala pang 5 secs eh I broke down in front of her. Cried so hard that I can't even breathe that time. It felt like all my sorrows for the past years rushed out from my inside. So shocked si mama kasi di nya alam napano ako

I hated myself to the point na wala binitawan ko na lahat. I assumed na lahat ng tao sa mundo eh ayaw na sakin. So 30 mins passed nung nangyari yun eh napagisipan kong pumunta kay sa bahay nina mama to say goodbye na sana. I asked my big bro na ihatid ako dun

So march 11 na and same shit parin. Nung gumabi na eh dun na nangyari lahat. I got triggered by something and i choked my lil bro so hard. Sinama ni mama yung kapatid ko sa pag uwi and ako eh pumuntang kwarto narin. Kinain na naman ako ng konsensya. Asked myself bat ako ganun

Naglaslas ng konti tas ayun dumugo nga and then nung March 10 ng gabi eh napagdesisyunan ko na talagang magpakamatay. 99% sure nako that time pero yung 1% eh di ko pa binitawan. Sinabi ko na I'll wait for another day tas tignan ko if may mangyari na makakapagbago ng lahat

So 1st week ng march eh sobrang lala ng episode ko. Panic attacks, anxiety, depression etc. As in sobrang lala. Dami kong nadamay na tao, madaming nadamay na mga bagay. Iyak lang ako ng iyak, di kumakain ng tama at di narin natutulog halos.

Everytime na ma dodown ako sa sarili ko eh palagi yung nangyari ang ginagawa kong dahilan to lower myself pa. Pag may nakitang video na about mom eh nalulungkot ako at naiiyak pero di parin ako nag sorry at hinayaan nalang to the point na di ko na talaga kinaya

Since wala nakong ma tweet eh share ko nalang yung experience ko last week. So I've been hunted by my guilt for 5 years na dahil sa ginawa ko kay mama dati. I never apologized for it and never na din namin na mention yung nangyari We let time heal kaso di ko kinaya yung konsensya
